page.title: 05MY HOME IN MILTON KEYNES
page.content: Great Linford is quite a big place. In Walshes Manor where I live there is only one house which is empty out of about 222 houses. If I want to play out on swings I can just go out of the back door; there is a playground on my left and right. There is a shop just at the end of the street and just a bit further away is a school. I pass the shop every morning to get to school. Also there is a pond with fish, newts, frogs and tadpoles. There are many kinds of fish in the pond. Just at the side of the pond is bus stop.
